assets.name: assets/5_Ymw_DN3Tt
assets.description: My second fantasy environment. This one is very large, you'll have to 'swim' around the environment to see everything. The world features two swimmers, an undersea world featuring a giant sea creature, some caverns and a weedy sea bed. In the mountains a man stands on a perilous bridge and beyond that a winding road is littered with travellers. Far above are several planets and stars.
